Introduction

Candy Shop is a five member girl group under Brave Entertainment. They made their debut on March 27, 2024 with the mini album "Hashtag#".

On May 8, Brave Entertainment announced that member Yuina would temporarily suspend activities due to health issues and that a new member will be recruited. On May 14, Julia was announced as the new member.
